  "subdivision_of_building": "The proposal will only affect the ground floor of the building. We propose to turn the premises into a nail and beauty salon. It will comprise of the following:\n\n1. A glass store front with an entrance in the centre.\n\n2. Space for a reception desk.\n\n3. An area for clients to wait their turn for service.\n\n4. 3 double nail treatment tables, capable of dealing with 6 clients at a time.\n\n5. A dedicated pedicure area with 3 pedicure chairs.\n\n6. A separate room at the rear of the premises for beauty treatments.\n\n7. A filtered ventilation system to extract fumes, nails and dust from the salon and away from the tenants in the upper floors.\n\n8. LED lights to provide comfortable ambient lighting.\n\n9. A small kitchen.\n\n10. A lavatory with wash basin.\n\n11. A utility room to store all chemical substances and cleaning materials away from clients and staff. This room will also incorporate a washing machine and sink to clean towels and salon equipment.",
